verbose_text: Following transplantation, the liver tissue and blood samples were collected on days 1, 3 and 7, we detected the EdU (5-ethynyl-2 '-deoxyuridine)-labeled cells homing to the liver tissue and assessed the proliferating cell nuclear antigen (PCNA) and cysteine containing aspartate specific protease (caspase) -3 expression in the liver tissue and detected the levels of stromal cell derived factor 1 (SDF-1) and hepatocyte growth factor (HGF) in the liver tissues.
